    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with this absolute gem of a car. It\u2019s been super reliable and is in really solid condition, perfect for anyone looking for a smooth, dependable ride that still looks great on the road. It\u2019s been well-cared for and is totally ready for its next owner to jump in and go! Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it\u2014I'd love to show you around your potential new ride!",
