    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock. Crucially, the subframe has been reinforced and the VANOS system serviced, addressing the primary technical concerns of this chassis. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and patina indicative of a well-loved driver's car, the suspension kinematics remain tight and the engine provides linear, aspirated power across the entire rev range. A robust, performance-ready machine for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
