      "description": "This distinguished vehicle represents a superb marriage of performance and value. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable condition, it offers a refined cabin environment and a robust service history. This is an exceptional opportunity for the professional seeking a reliable, high-caliber driving experience without compromise.",
      "price": 36500.0,
