    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's honestly been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my daily trips. The engine runs smoothly, the interior is nice and comfy, and it still looks great parked in the driveway! It\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner. If you're looking for a reliable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love it!",
      "price": 32000.0,
