    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The powertrain delivers exceptional throttle response via individual throttle bodies, while the Variable M Differential Lock ensures optimal power delivery through the rear wheels. This car has been maintained with technical precision, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The suspension geometry remains tight, offering the balanced handling and communicative steering feedback synonymous with the M-division's peak naturally aspirated era.",
